Underwater basket weaving
Main Skill: Crafting
Max Efficiency: 180%

You deftly weave the thin pieces of coral into a basket. The process is slow and tedious, but the end result fills your heart with pride of your creation.

The Underwater basket weaving activity is a Crafting activity.

Location

This activity can be done at the following location:

  • Elara's Lagoon in Syrenthia

Requirements

Skill Level Requirements:

  • At least Crafting lvl. 40.

Keyword Requirements:

  • Requires [3] unique Diving gear equipped.

Visibility

This activity is always visible.
